at.ac.tuwien.dsg.cloud.elise.master.RESTService

Interface UnitInstanceDAO


  • public interface UnitInstanceDAO
    The APIs enables to read/write/search unit instances in ELISE. These APIs only query information in the database without any execution for collecting real information. For the information collecting, please use communication service APIs.
    Author:
    Duc-Hung Le
